Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:15.82,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Claudio...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:17.83,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Think you could take off...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:25.33,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,your glasses for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:28.56,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.56,0:00:31.09,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Here is tonight's dolce.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:37.83,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,How did you know that today was my birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:42.97,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I heard it from a customer here, one year ago today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.89,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I remember it was raining that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:49.85,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You were with some close friends, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:52.07,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You remembered that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:55.10,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I'm glad it's not raining this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:58.32,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:02.14,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.57,0:01:06.83,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Another year has come and gone, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:10.22,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Indeed it has. You're welcome to stop by any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:18.04,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,This mysterious restaurant is on a road just a little ways from the center of Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:09.31,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, if that's the place you're looking for,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:12.78,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,just take a left at that corner and it's right up the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:14.17,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:16.09,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Do you have a reservation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:20.04,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It's a popular spot, so you probably won't get seated without one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.45,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:25.72,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It's really that popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:46.37,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Ristorante casetta dell'orso...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:49.04,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.68,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:06.14,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:12.93,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Do you have a reservation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:16.32,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:21.19,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I'm afraid we're entirely booked tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.40,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:27.16,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Is the owner in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.69,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He should be here any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:32.58,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Forgive me, but who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:35.90,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Well... I'm the daughter of an acquaintance of his!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:40.80,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,In that case, please have a seat and wait over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:42.50,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:47.43,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Allow me to take your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:50.37,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.35,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:57.06,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Is this your first time in Rome?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:04:59.62,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,My first since I was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.19,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I was actually born here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.52,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.23,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I really came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:26.34,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:29.80,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,My, he looks so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:32.93,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:42.07,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,They're all older men with spectacles...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.71,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What kind of restaurant is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.90,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:53.20,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You have a guest waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:54.29,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:57.21,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Who might it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:08.67,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:12.22,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I have something to tell the owner - your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:18.04,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,About the fact you're really a divorcee with a twenty-one year old daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:20.80,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Oh no, you don't! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.86,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I could care less what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:25.81,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Listen to what your mother says!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:28.69,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I've never once thought of you as my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:34.28,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Fine. Then you aren't my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:43.37,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,How about you take this conversation inside? You two must be cold out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:44.85,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Be right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:45.66,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:55.46,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Look, just leave me alone tonight. We'll talk this over tomorrow, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:56.62,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:03.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I've really never considered her my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:08.63,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She got divorced from my father fifteen years ago and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:13.49,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She left me at my grandmother's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:18.02,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Look, Mommy really wants to get married to someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:22.75,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,but he told me he won't get married to someone who's been divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.36,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,So you understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:26.63,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:28.83,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'll come back to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:33.91,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Ciao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:43.83,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I can literally count the number of times she actually came to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:46.82,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I grew up without ever saying a word about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:50.01,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,but I've run out of patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.76,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm gonna tell him tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:55.66,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Nicoletta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.94,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You're quieter than usual tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:02.16,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, this is that 1994 I ordered last month...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.35,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Guess again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.75,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He seems a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:10.59,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,So, how do you two know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.86,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Umm, the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.24,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She's Nicoletta, the daughter of a friend of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:17.18,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She's on vacation here in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:17.99,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:21.68,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take good care of her while she's in town!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.11,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.11,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,My mother would be so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:36.26,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:40.52,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,This is the man from before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:44.00,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Yes, this is our head cameriere, Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.97,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,This is Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:49.36,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,She's the daughter of one of Olga's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:52.11,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Seems she's sightseeing here in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:55.88,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I see. So that's how you know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.26,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Th-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:01.97,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,This is tonight's antipasto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:09.31,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He's so graceful in his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:13.60,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Please take your time to savor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:18.34,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I see. He's a real gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.45,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.19,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What kind of restaurant is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:28.65,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Everyone's got googly-eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:32.85,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:36.55,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Yes, our chef is quite talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.87,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,No wonder it's popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:42.13,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,When I walked in, they told me I'd need a reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:46.98,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Yes, most of our customers come to pursue the waitstaff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.44,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:51.50,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We get bombarded with women infatuated with real gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:53.61,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It's like this every single night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:59.73,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It's like a different world to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:03.25,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:07.76,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We have a customer who doesn't eat beef,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:11.16,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,so please prepare one portion of the antipasto accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:12.45,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:18.08,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Miss, the restroom is the door to your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:19.08,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.97,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, this is our chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:29.65,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,The antipasto was fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:31.25,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.69,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Another pair of spectacles...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:40.53,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Spectacles must be required wear here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:46.61,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I suppose you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:50.21,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You won't be hired here if you don't wear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:51.11,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:53.54,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,My vision is fine, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:55.46,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.46,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.91,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,They're just for show.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:10:57.96,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.93,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Madam prefers it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.93,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Madam prefers it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.39,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Pr-Prefers it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:09.73,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What kind of restaurant is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:30.37,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Man, she really pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:36.92,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Having all that fun living here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:42.46,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.35,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Nicoletta? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:48.37,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I know I promised we'd talk today, but something came up and I can't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:52.02,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'll call you when I finish setting you up with the apartment today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.46,Ristorante,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:52.41,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.31,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:57.55,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,All she thinks about is herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:27.12,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm lucky that she'll loan me an apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But what should I do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.82,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:46.51,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Isn't that the head cameriere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:51.71,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Ciao.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:53.91,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Buon giorno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:56.76,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Buon giorno, Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:58.42,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Out for a stroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:01.29,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He's kinda sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:09.50,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,If I had time, I'd love to show you around town a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:12.85,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I have to get to the restaurant already...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:17.72,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, if you haven't eaten yet, why don't you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:19.87,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But I don't have a reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:22.94,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You can have some of the food they give the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:26.59,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It's actually about as good as the stuff on the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:31.82,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, perhaps it was rude of me to invite you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:36.57,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Not at all. I want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:42.88,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,The owner asked me to show you\Na good time while you're here in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:50.61,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Just what did the owner see in her that made him want to marry her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.51,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Wanting to be surrounded by bespectacled men...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.47,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Always pushing her selfish demands...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:59.98,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I understand the owner's feelings quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:03.65,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He wants to make her happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.01,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,She's a lovely lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:08.82,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:10.77,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Why did I say "Eh"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:15.91,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.32,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,This is a bustling town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:25.26,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,But try and fall in love with Rome as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.64,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.59,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:05.71,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:11.30,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Please, allow me to introduce you to everyone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:17.65,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,This is dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:24.45,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:25.65,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Prego.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:40.08,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Say, who's the most popular among you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:44.13,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Well, that's gotta be Luciano.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.48,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I'd say Vito.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:53.01,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,No, Teo has all the women waiting with bated breath for him to come out of the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:55.61,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Well, I'm gonna have to say Furio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:59.85,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm disqualified for wearing fake spectacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:06.36,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,How about you, Claudio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:08.86,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:12.61,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,All the first-time customers like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.99,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,But there are others who are more popular with the regulars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:20.10,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,That's not to say he isn't popular with them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:21.62,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:24.91,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Because he's serious, he keeps his urges to himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:26.72,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,and... look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:33.78,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Vito and Furio are wearing rings too,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:37.11,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,but they don't act as serious about it as Claudio does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:41.01,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,How can I say no to a beautiful woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:46.17,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,And Furio gives cooking lessons to women.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:49.07,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,At home, on days when the restaurant is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.94,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It's nothing special, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.24,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.73,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Luciano is a widower.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:57.07,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He's always got a sour expression,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:17:00.33,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,but there are some women who can't get enough of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:04.83,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Lunch today is a little too salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:07.00,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Which one of you bums made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:12.42,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,See. All that complaining is aging you quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:17.28,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,So you see, we're all unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:23.09,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Though we didn't get popular until word got out about all the spectacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.74,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Umm, what about Gigi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:36.66,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, Gigi doesn't socialize much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.41,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,No, he doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.49,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.39,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.49,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Now that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:54.30,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Well, I was a bit uncomfortable with how we attract so many strange customers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.51,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,But we got over that quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:59.42,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,And of course, we have people who come for the food, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:01.48,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,They come for Teo's dolce, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.26,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You're too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:14.46,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It's just whatever furniture was lying around,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:16.46,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,so let me know if there's anything else you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:31.46,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right, her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:35.33,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Every birthday, when I was a little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:38.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Grazie, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:50.77,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Well, there's nothing wrong with being sent gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:19:00.61,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Welcome to Rome - Olga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.73,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Buonasera, Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:23.30,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Is she going to be all right all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.36,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,She can stay with us as often as she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:29.88,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Thanks, but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:31.52,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:36.54,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You're cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:39.28,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Let's go warm up at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:42.53,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I wonder if everyone will be wearing glasses again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:51.72,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:54.19,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Nice greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:57.21,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, things just prettied up around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:04.31,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sheesh, this isn't a playground for kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:06.62,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I don't care if you're friends with the Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:09.37,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Kids these days, I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:06.57,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I have to say, I'm starting to like this place, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:09.37,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Though I haven't developed a spectacles-fetish yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:11.89,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm different from those other women.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:13.95,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:19.68,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I really like that one gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:27.59,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,The restaurant is located on a street in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:30.29,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Its name is casetta dell'orso.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:33.70,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It means "a bear's tiny house."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.06,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Was that her idea, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.35,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I mustn't!
